OL,7,FPc Stephen Smith, 51, and Pc Rachel
OL,8,FComotto, 36, are on trial at Southwark
OL,9,FCrown Court accused of assault
OL,10,Foccasioning actual bodily harm after
OL,11,Fallegedly using excessive force on Mr
OL,12,FBurgess in June 2022.
OL,14,FSmith is charged with two counts of
OL,15,Fassault, relating to his use of Pava
OL,16,Fspray and a baton, while Comotto faces
OL,17,Fone count for discharging her Taser.
