OL,7,FEarlier this week, jurors heard how
OL,8,FSmith allegedly emptied a full
OL,9,Fcanister of the incapacitant into Mr
OL,10,FBurgess's face, struck him with a
OL,11,Fbaton, and how Comotto deployed her
OL,12,FTaser ` all within 83 seconds of
OL,13,Fentering his room.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, the jury was shown fresh
OL,16,Fbody-worn camera footage from the
OL,17,Faftermath of the incident.
OL,19,FIn one clip, Comotto is seen laughing
OL,20,Fand asking Smith: "Oh my God, is there
OL,21,Fany left in your can?"
