OL,7,FProsecutors say the force used against
OL,8,FMr Burgess ` who had been threatening
OL,9,Fstaff with a serrated cutlery knife
OL,10,Fand telling them he would take
OL,11,Fpleasure in murdering them ` was
OL,12,Fexcessive and unnecessary given his
OL,13,Fage and physical condition.
OL,15,FHe was seated in his wheelchair and
OL,16,Fsurrounded by staff when officers
OL,17,Fentered his room and began issuing
OL,18,Fcommands, jurors have heard.
