OL,16,Finterview and read to the court by
OL,17,Fprosecutor Paul Jarvis KC, the officer
OL,18,Fsaid: "Our objective was clear ` it
OL,19,Fwas to disarm Mr Burgess as quickly
OL,20,Fand safely as possible.
